            <h2>Welcome to <b>MS-CIT</b></h2>
            <p>MS-CIT (Maharashtra State Certificate in Information Technology) is an IT literacy course offered by MKCL (Maharashtra Knowledge Corporation Limited). It is designed to teach basic computer skills, digital literacy, and essential software usage.</p>
            <p><b>Who Should Take It?</b><ul>Beginners who want to learn computers</ul>
                <ul>Students looking for government-recognized IT certification</ul>
                <ul>Job seekers needing basic computer literacy</ul></p>
